The paper discusses privacy concerns related to personal profiling by online systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of machine learning algorithms to detect sensitive topics also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The practical tools proposed in the paper could also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI).
